"possible input values between :ref:`min "
"<class_VisualShaderNodeIntUniform_property_min>` and :ref:`max "
"<class_VisualShaderNodeIntUniform_property_max>`. Translated to "
"``hint_range(min, max)`` in shader code."
msgstr ""

